body:
@aselle given you support [sparse variable updates](https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.11/api_docs/python/state_ops.html#sparse-variable-updates) and your optimizers have [_apply_sparse](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/training/adam.py#L141) functionality.

It would be much appreciated if you could elaborate on the current state of sparse support for optimizers in TensorFlow and which challenges exists for implementing fully sparse support?

Thanks
